{"tid":1688282,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港POPO運用武力粗暴干預選舉","createTime":"2019-11-02T11:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T04:35:11.000Z","uid":46688,"like":98,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"f79188de425cd87d3d06ecbed16dc9ce285ecaf1","tid":1688282,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:01:30.000Z","msg":"Twitter Reddit plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n選舉為最基本民主要素<br />\n<br />\n外面唔同人可能睇唔清楚議會制度or種票問題<br />\n<br />\n但係我諗今日干預嘅行為係最能夠顯示俾外界<br />\n香港選舉制度完全失效，政府運用市民賦予權力<br />\n運用POPO干預<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己建議：有冇啲比較出名嘅團體可以有一份比較莊重嘅聲明，直接對外界宣布香港選舉制度失效，又或者可以搞多次世界各地嘅登報，對外宣布<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢度大家應該會話，香港選舉制度其實實效左好多年，依家先失效咩？<br />\n<br />\n如果對於香港人來講其實大家都知，但外界來講，佢哋可能根本上唔知或者唔能夠深入了解，但係今次係最簡單顯得出干預選舉嘅行為，所以唔可以令手足白白犧牲，把握今次機會。<br />\n<br />\n已經有三位候選人被捕，仲有數多位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12aafd0e2784bd2dad7ccb47b31edfee82ad4fb","tid":1688282,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2abd0c57ce172ab73b377b1fd3f967af21e545b","tid":1688282,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64cb97ee1e4ba6e409cc6f6f9bcf1d8110957646","tid":1688282,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T11:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"h